{
  "name": "equities_monthly_v32_leader_exhaustion_repair",
  "description": "Equities v32: same strong monthly sleeve, but explicitly try to avoid buying late exhausted leaders. Shorten hold horizon a bit, raise momentum-quality gates, and search a tighter pullback window while keeping TOP_N=2 and the existing correlation/cluster defenses.",
